name: Suzani Bubabni
description: Well I am a very easygoing person, I think of others way before myself, if I’m out with someone its important to me that they are having a good time, I am very confident, I always know what I want in life. I rarely give in, and see things though. i want a man we will start the dream life together and make the best enviable home together because all i just want is to be happy and make my man happy too and be proud of him..
